    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/853ff611cea0e53719fcd52bb1af9c91.avif?t=1742379127\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope Brown, apprentice sheriff of Hudrence County, after the outbreak of the epidemic he travels to Micido, his hometown, to look for his brother, the only member of his family alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, however, you will encounter various difficulties including: zombies, monsters, assassins and criminals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to find out who is the mind that designed this virus to eliminate the population? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your exploration you will meet characters who will change your life, you will discover crimes and hidden truths.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEWARE OF THE DARK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/9e4b5ec1663f4c3295e6e2ac3fcdd5c2.poster.avif?t=1742379127\" width=800 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/9e4b5ec1663f4c3295e6e2ac3fcdd5c2.webm?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/9e4b5ec1663f4c3295e6e2ac3fcdd5c2.mp4?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The torch will be essential, many places will be in darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENEMY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/33d6a45f52b0cd6737df270e865da81c.poster.avif?t=1742379127\" width=800 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/33d6a45f52b0cd6737df270e865da81c.webm?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/33d6a45f52b0cd6737df270e865da81c.mp4?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful who you meet, monsters and zombies will never be your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FRIENDS OR NOT?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/a3979be71cebf61f6114e871e1dee203.poster.avif?t=1742379127\" width=800 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/a3979be71cebf61f6114e871e1dee203.webm?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320960/extras/a3979be71cebf61f6114e871e1dee203.mp4?t=1742379127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may meet friendly survivors who will help you, but be careful not to trust of all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose whether or not to help other survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the right weapon for your style.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main story but also with side missions.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the dark secrets of the virus.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INVESTIGATE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock secret rooms.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to unlock secrets.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find special items.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the survivors to find out their story and that of the virus.</p></li></ul>",
